        "email": "jsimmons@infradead.org",
        "username": "jsimmons"
      },
      "date": "2015-07-03 18:12:53.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nUsing internal linux kernel headers in user land is considered a no no.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "e06f22a82e69828df992cebc04c5a50b221912ca",
