        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2015-07-03 19:34:56.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nAFAIK they are used by e2fsprogs, and we don't need to worry about building on non-Linux platforms anymore.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
