      },
      "date": "2016-01-08 17:33:04.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI started to look into what is required to use the linux/list.h header. We will need to include the path of the linux kernel development header for all our utilities to make that work. It can be done especially for libraries. Lustre test applications and utilities not dependent on any libraries I can't see that being the case.",
